    "BiCNet [49] and MS-MARL-GCM [87] are evaluated on an early version of StarCraft [95].",
    "Then, a new version of StarCraft, SMAC, has become popular in recent works [30-32, 65, 74, 93].",
    "By controlling a team of agents, the cooperative goal in SMAC is to defeat enemies on easy, hard, and super hard maps.",
    "Net [93] and MAIC are two recent works that surpass multiple communication methods and value decomposition methods (e.g., QMIX) on different maps.",
    "Google research football [98] is an even more challenging game with a physics-based 3D soccer simulator."
